OL,5, More than 60,000 adults with           
OL,6, disabilities and long-term illnesses in
OL,7, England were chased for debts by       
OL,8, councils last year after failing to pay
OL,9, for their social care support at home. 
OL,11,FClaimants told the BBC they can't      
OL,12,Fafford the charges amid rising food and
OL,13,Frent prices, along with the additional 
OL,14,Fcosts of living with disabilities.     
OL,16,FCouncils took legal action against 330 
OL,17,Fpeople in 2021-22.                     
OL,19,FThe Local Government Association said  
OL,20,Fsuch action was a "last option".       
